      "id": "PopularPost121837",
      "post_content": "Interesting, but not true. The \"Heck cattle\" was created by the zoo directors Heinz and Lutz Heck for the mentioned reason but they weren't Nazis. It was in the 1920s when there wasn't a Nazi-dictatorship in Germany. Therefore the cattle wasn't used for propaganda.",
